<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="10"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> muṉaiveṉṟiyuṭaiyāṉ cōḻa cēntaṉ kōṉṉum pāṟppaṭu miku patiyōr mutal pallōrkaḷu maḷamut<unclear>tiya</unclear> vilaiyāvaṇam Ulakaṟiya viḷaṅku vittipperuntaṉa<unclear>ṉā</unclear> miccilaiyā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ḷar pukaḻkūlic cēvakarē karampatākki kāciniyil nilainiṟuttiya kārāḷaṉ kuṟaṇṭi kāvalaṉ pēcariya yiṭattuvaḷi pērāḷaṉ kumpaṉūr mutal kuṉṟattūr
<lb n="12"/>puttūr <unclear>vaṭa</unclear>kulattimutal kōḷun teṉṟal maṉṟattūriḷamaturaimaṉ peruntu vaḷivanta koṇṭalvāḻi kuṇavāṉ payanta neṭuvēṟccāttaṉ kuṭipō
<lb n="13" break="no"/>la cīritalla Ulakuyarnta tūṇāki Ōṅkiyē malantu mikucimaiyattu vaṭaperumāllē §
</p>

